This topic describes how to use Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) Ops Manager to configure the BOSH Director on Azure Government Cloud.

First, complete the steps in [Prepare Azure](./azure-prepare-env.html) and [Deploying BOSH and Ops Manager to Azure Manually](./azure-om-deploy.html).

Then, follow the procedure for a manual Azure install. In the procedure, be sure to select **Azure Government Cloud** in the **Azure Environment** dropdown and set custom VM types.

For the installation procedure, see [Configuring Ops Manager on Azure](azure-om-config.html).